response.overview: Game Master Video Vol.9 Super Street Fighter 2X  COLOR/100min/STEREO/ June 11th 1994  Shinseisha GV-009  I came here... to defeat the strongest man, to overcome everything,  The "Street Fighter I and II" series, a pioneer of fighting games  Many super combos are included. The game master staff has put all their effort into making this into a video! This is the 5th installment of "Super Street Fighter Street Fighter IX"  All-inclusive! The Super Street Fighter IX vs. Gouki battle held on May 3rd was also fully covered with all characters, and in addition to computer battles and battles,  It also includes the heated battles from the national tournament.  This guy is really hot!
